data.description: Want a new home for Christmas then why wait for a new build when you can buy this desired five-level split today?  You'll enjoy the large size of this home.  It boasts an enormous fully equipped kitchen with a center island, pantry, gas range, and eating space.  Enjoy the much-needed den/office space, two living spaces, soaring ceilings, light and bright, freshly painted, four large bedrooms (w/walk-in closets), 2.5 baths, a 2nd-floor laundry room, and incredible outside living space.  Located on a cul-de-sac and located across the street from a great park for playing.  Don't wait ... it to see.  Call your agent today.A 2.25 VA loan that could be assumed by a veteran.
